            <p><abbr title="Kasiana Amara">Kasi</abbr> came to us with this project for the Macquarie University Hospital in Sydney. A small two page website which lead to an EventBrite page to buy tickets. Kasi was imagining a pretty animation heavy design to really bring the invite to life. It was under a pretty short deadline but we were excited so, elbows were greased. We didn't get that many projects that involved animation this heavily so it was a good opportunity to flex some creative muscles.</p>

            <p>Ok so the setup goes a little like this. We had a desktop mockup with a large raster image background. A couple of minor raster image assets and then rest of the items were vectors. One or two things we needed to cut out of the background and fill the background in a little.</p> 
